================ HERMES SERVER ================

1. What is it
   The great Messenger of the gods

2. Requirements
   - twisted-web
   - twisted-words

3. Installation
   Use distutils or emerge hermes on gentoo

4. Configuration
   Look data/hermes.xml. this file will be installed as defualt.
   default location /etc/hermes.xml may be overriden by hermes_CONFIG
   enronment variable

5. Starting
   "hermes" or "/etc/init.d/hermes start" on gentoo

6. Daemon listens port from configuration for incoming xml-rpc requests.
   and resends everything to apropriate contacts via xmpp or some other protocol
